ack dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white"><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">Unique and surprisingly fun</li><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">Plenty of entertainment choices between webOS apps, HDMI, and AirPlay</li><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">Speakers are actually good</li></ul></div><div class="border-t border-franklin pt-16 md:pt-0 [&amp;&gt;p]:mb-8 [&amp;&gt;ul&gt;li]:mb-6 [&amp;&gt;ul&gt;li]:leading-140 [&amp;&gt;ul]:my-0  [&amp;&gt;ul]:mb-16 [&amp;&gt;ul]:py-0 md:[&amp;&gt;ul]:mb-0 [&amp;_*]:font-polysans-mono  [&amp;_*]:text-14 [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black [&amp;_li]:marker:text-franklin [&amp;_p]:font-light [&amp;_strong]:font-medium [&amp;_ul]:font-light md:w-1/2 md:border-t-0 md:first:border-r md:first:pr-16 md:last:pl-16"><h3 class="mb-8 font-polysans-mono font-medium uppercase leading-140 tracking-12">The Bad</h3><ul class="duet--article--unordered-list my-20 list-disc pl-18 marker:text-blurple/100 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white"><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">It’s damn heavy</li><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">Unimpressive display specs for the price</li><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">Battery life can be an issue</li><li class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mb-16 pl-12 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1">No water resistance</li></ul></div></div><div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center px-24 md:flex-row md:flex-wrap md:justify-center md:px-0"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/LG-27-Inch-StanbyME-Portable-27LX5QKNA/dp/B0CF44ZMLG?tag=theverge02-20" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" data-item-id="10247" class="m-8 mb-12 flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-blurple p-8 text-center font-polysans-mono text-11 font-medium uppercase tracking-12 text-blurple shadow-[3px_4px] transition-all duration-[.1s] ease-in-out hover:shadow-[5px_6px] sm:max-w-[250px]">$1197 at Amazon</a><a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=1025X1701640&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.skimresources.com%3Fid%3D1025X1701640%26xs%3D1%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%252Fc%252Fproduct%252F1775282-REG%252Flg_27lx5qkna_standbyme_go_27_full.html" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" data-item-id="10247" class="m-8 mb-12 flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-blurple p-8 text-center font-polysans-mono text-11 font-medium uppercase tracking-12 text-blurple shadow-[3px_4px] transition-all duration-[.1s] ease-in-out hover:shadow-[5px_6px] sm:max-w-[250px]">$1197 at B&amp;H Photo</a><a href="https://howl.me/clV13ANbq81" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" data-item-id="10247" class="m-8 mb-12 flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-sm border border-blurple p-8 text-center font-polysans-mono text-11 font-medium uppercase tracking-12 text-blurple shadow-[3px_4px] transition-all duration-[.1s] ease-in-out hover:shadow-[5px_6px] sm:max-w-[250px]">$1200 at Best Buy</a></div></aside><div class="mb-40 flex justify-center font-polysans-mono text-12 font-light text-blurple dark:text-franklin"><a title="How we rate and review products" class="border-b" href="/pages/how-we-rate">How we rate and review products</a></div></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup duet--article--standard-paragraph mb-20 font-fkroman text-18 leading-160 -tracking-1 selection:bg-franklin-20 dark:text-white dark:selection:bg-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-highlight-blurple [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-black dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-white">Aside from its heft, the biggest thing going against the StanbyME Go is the $1,200 that LG is asking for what, at the end of the day, is a pretty unremarkable 27-inch LCD panel. It’s a 1080p screen with so-so viewing angles and a peak brightness of 500 nits. That’s more than fine for indoor viewing, and I’ve also found it adequate for most outdoor usage so long as you’re not in direct sunlight. (The display’s anti-reflective coating helps out here big time.) But if you’re judging this thing by display specs alone, paying $1,200 for it would be lunacy. I would go wild for a 4K OLED version of the StanbyME Go, though that would likely rocket its price up into $2,000 territory. The nicheness of this product is inherently part of why it’s more expensive than many would prefer.</p></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component clear-both block w-full md:ml-[-100px] md:w-outdent"><div class="my-9"><div class="transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"><div class="fixed inset-0 h-[110vh] w-full bg-white transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out z-[-1] cursor-default opacity-0" role="button" aria-label="Close" tabindex="0"></div><div role="button" aria-label="Zoom" tabindex="0" class="visible z-30 w-full origin-center transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-zoom-in"><figure class="transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out lg:mx-0"><div><div class="duet--media--content-warning relative" style="padding-top:66.66666666666666%"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="A photo of LG’s Stanby